# hexa-lang /.chain — chain definitions (raw#0 forward-chain)
# format: `chain <id> <status> "<name>"` + column-2 key/value pairs
# status (4, locked): live | paused | planned | deferred
#
# keys (whitelist):
#   step.<id>.cmd <command...>       — shell/stage0 command for that step
#   step.<id>.timeout <seconds>       — optional hard timeout (default 600)
#   mode <strict|loose>               — prev-marker guard policy
#   ttl  <seconds>                    — marker TTL (default 3600)
#   why  <text>                       — free-form description
#
# semantics (enforced by tool/chain_runner.hexa):
#   · user triggers any step; downstream steps then auto-cascade
#   · strict mode requires all earlier step_<id>_ok markers to exist
#   · loose mode skips prev-marker check (entry from any step)
#   · marker files live under .chain-state/<chain_id>/ and are chflags uchg
#     locked on macOS (kernel EPERM). Linux sandbox = best-effort chattr +i.
#   · any step failure cancels the remaining downstream cascade.

chain 1 live "release"
  step.build.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/build_stage0.hexa
  step.verify.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/raw_all.hexa
  step.fixpoint.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/verify_fixpoint.hexa
  step.archive.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/fixpoint_archive.hexa snapshot
  mode strict
  ttl 7200
  why build → verify → fixpoint → archive 자동 연쇄. entry 자유.

chain 2 live "daily-check"
  step.raw_all.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/raw_all.hexa
  step.fixpoint.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/verify_fixpoint.hexa --quick
  step.audit_check.cmd ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/raw_audit.hexa verify
  mode strict
  ttl 3600
  why .loop 에서 매일 트리거. drift 자동 감지.
